import React from 'react'

export const PieChartLegend = (data) => {
  const { style, x, y } = data
    console.log(data)
  const sum = data.data[0].number + data.data[1].number
  console.log(sum, x ,y)
  return (
    <svg>
      <g>
        <ellipse cx={x} cy={y-27} rx="14" ry="7" fill={style.fill} />
      </g>
      <text fontSize="25" x={x+300} y={y+7}>
        {data.datum.number}
      </text>
      
      <text x={x+27} y={y + 30} fontSize={25}>
        {data.datum.number /100} %
      </text>
     
    </svg >
  )
}
